===Indications===
* {{note|narina|1}} If <span style="font-size:140%;">{{lang|ps|ى}}</span> follows a consonant in a word, it indicates the word is [[Grammatical gender|masculine]] [[Grammatical number|singular]] and in the [[direct case]].
* {{note|khezina|2}} <span style="font-size:140%;">{{lang|ps|ۍ}}</span> always indicates the word it occurs in is feminine.
* {{note|failiya|3}} If <span style="font-size:140%;">{{lang|ar|ئ}}</span> occurs at the end of a verb, it indicates the verb is in [[Grammatical person|second person]] [[Grammatical number|plural]] form. Note, that sometimes the grammatical <span style="font-size:140%;">{{lang|ar|ئ}}</span> was lacked either in the typing as in the alphabet and replaced with the <span style="font-size:140%;">{{lang|ps|ۍ}}</span>.

